  "detailed_description": "<h1>Run your own supermarket!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/89991e29886bca7a66d7f361f552febc.avif?t=1772361673\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run your own supermarket! Buy, stock, and sell items, expand your store, and manage customers. Customize your layout, explore new locations, and hire staff. Keep things fresh with variety and new challenges as you grow your business.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Store Management</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/158c4cdbd74ab1ec276d9b8ccc2981a6.poster.avif?t=1772361673\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/158c4cdbd74ab1ec276d9b8ccc2981a6.webm?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/158c4cdbd74ab1ec276d9b8ccc2981a6.mp4?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design your store to balance efficiency and aesthetics. Arrange product displays, organize aisles, and create a seamless shopping experience for your customers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Supply Goods</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/1b793bda6dcbd1eeed4f08867cae363f.poster.avif?t=1772361673\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/1b793bda6dcbd1eeed4f08867cae363f.webm?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/1b793bda6dcbd1eeed4f08867cae363f.mp4?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the in-game computer to order stock, unpack goods, organize your storage, and stock shelves, fridges, and freezers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cashier</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/532846cd63a628078b3b10f1e15f58a1.poster.avif?t=1772361673\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/532846cd63a628078b3b10f1e15f58a1.webm?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/532846cd63a628078b3b10f1e15f58a1.mp4?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scan items, process cash and card payments, and make sure customers enjoy a smooth and satisfying checkout experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Free Market</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/a138183388bf0dd8f02bebdbf81db6a7.poster.avif?t=1772361673\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/a138183388bf0dd8f02bebdbf81db6a7.webm?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/a138183388bf0dd8f02bebdbf81db6a7.mp4?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage a dynamic real-time market. Purchase products at low prices and set optimal selling prices to maximize profits while keeping customers happy.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/065dca5f92f9e6768f0c5794144d53cf.poster.avif?t=1772361673\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/065dca5f92f9e6768f0c5794144d53cf.webm?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/065dca5f92f9e6768f0c5794144d53cf.mp4?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reinvest your profits to grow your business. Expand your store, upgrade interiors, and stay ahead of the ever-changing demands of the retail market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Supermarket Simulator Pro, every decision counts. Can you turn a small store into a thriving retail empire while balancing customer satisfaction and managing your finances?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run your own supermarket! Buy, stock, and sell items, expand your store, and manage customers. Customize your layout, explore new locations, and hire staff. Keep things fresh with variety and new challenges as you grow your business.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Store Management</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/158c4cdbd74ab1ec276d9b8ccc2981a6.poster.avif?t=1772361673\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/158c4cdbd74ab1ec276d9b8ccc2981a6.webm?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/158c4cdbd74ab1ec276d9b8ccc2981a6.mp4?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design your store to balance efficiency and aesthetics. Arrange product displays, organize aisles, and create a seamless shopping experience for your customers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Supply Goods</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/1b793bda6dcbd1eeed4f08867cae363f.poster.avif?t=1772361673\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/1b793bda6dcbd1eeed4f08867cae363f.webm?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/1b793bda6dcbd1eeed4f08867cae363f.mp4?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the in-game computer to order stock, unpack goods, organize your storage, and stock shelves, fridges, and freezers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cashier</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/532846cd63a628078b3b10f1e15f58a1.poster.avif?t=1772361673\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/532846cd63a628078b3b10f1e15f58a1.webm?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/532846cd63a628078b3b10f1e15f58a1.mp4?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scan items, process cash and card payments, and make sure customers enjoy a smooth and satisfying checkout experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Free Market</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/a138183388bf0dd8f02bebdbf81db6a7.poster.avif?t=1772361673\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/a138183388bf0dd8f02bebdbf81db6a7.webm?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/a138183388bf0dd8f02bebdbf81db6a7.mp4?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage a dynamic real-time market. Purchase products at low prices and set optimal selling prices to maximize profits while keeping customers happy.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/065dca5f92f9e6768f0c5794144d53cf.poster.avif?t=1772361673\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/065dca5f92f9e6768f0c5794144d53cf.webm?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398140/extras/065dca5f92f9e6768f0c5794144d53cf.mp4?t=1772361673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reinvest your profits to grow your business. Expand your store, upgrade interiors, and stay ahead of the ever-changing demands of the retail market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Supermarket Simulator Pro, every decision counts. Can you turn a small store into a thriving retail empire while balancing customer satisfaction and managing your finances?</p>",
